{"tid":317631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［網頁遊戲］deeeep.io 深海大作戰","createTime":"2017-07-11T14:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T15:57:17.000Z","uid":56875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81a686ff8a6a1a26fab69aae00bb07dde333d3b4","tid":317631,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:40:03.000Z","msg":"深海大作戰玩法係控制一隻生物，係弱肉強食世界裡生存同成長。<br />\n<br />\n玩既巴打，麻煩改名時加HKG開頭，方便相認同唔好打自己友。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://deeeep.io/beta\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdeeeep.io%2Fbeta&d=5WjZKLTINK2qf%2ByFkRl3IS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=ac4e4d51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://deeeep.io/beta</a><br />\nAsia 1 server<br />\n<br />\n我個名：HKG ████████████████<br />\n<br />\n今晚要攻占海洋區(地圖中間位置) <br />\n<br />\n簡介一下隻game<br />\n海域分4個，最左係北極，中間係海洋，中下係深海，最右係淡水。<br />\n<br />\n每個物種進化路線都唔同，面每個區既物種都有限制，例如深海唔可以去淺水區，淡水魚唔可以去海。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩推post"},{"pid":"cd21b925b852f533d9e488af7afddd84f66e73c2","tid":317631,"uid":67686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"78324ec9de8f1999c7192b4778b981beb0ab168d","tid":317631,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pish</blockquote><br />\nThx, 等緊各位巴打一齊玩"},{"pid":"f789de67d60de047592d3b41b29a6428655bc9f0","tid":317631,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5f3841ee11fa8158648d60de878280a93bc7e4","tid":317631,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00e925b13f0805488f9132601b8e93d5e6787b4","tid":317631,"uid":86740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:50:21.000Z","msg":"join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=